T01D1168:240b-1: aashta ma h'a sth'a na tsee ta ban da n'a ma sta ba:/
T01D1168:240b-3: gnas chen po brgyad kyi mchod rten la phyag 'tshal ba'i bstod pa //
T01D1168:240b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01D1168:240b-5: bltams dang byang chub mnyam med chos kyi 'khor lo dge ba bskor //
T01D1168:240b-6: mchod rten thog mar 'jig rten gsum mchod dang ldan cho 'phrul chen po dang //
T01D1168:240b-7: gang ri'i kha dog ltar gsal lha las babs pa'i gnas 'di dang //
T01D1168:240b-8: gang du bde gshegs mya ngan 'das pa de la spyi bos bdag phyag 'tshal //
T01D1168:240b-9: yangs can w'a r'a na s'i byis pa gsod ri 'jigs rungs bcings 'gram dang //
T01D1168:241a-0: mnyan yod dang ni byang chub shing @241a * //
T01D1168:241a-1: drung ku sha'i srong mchog ser skya lumbi n'i //
T01D1168:241a-2: koo shambi dang mdzod mthug mnyam pa'i grong mchog dpa' skyong yul 'khor dang //
T01D1168:241a-3: stobs bcu ldan pa'i mchod rten gzhan gang yin pa de la'ang spyis phyag 'tshal //
T01D1168:241a-4: kha che dang ni rgya yul khab ya mun zhes pa dang //
T01D1168:241a-5: singga la dang ao te sindhu shing 'phal ba ga mang ba kha ko la //
T01D1168:241a-6: bal yul k'a ma r'u dang bum pa'i klong mchog k'anytsi bzang po'i yul //
T01D1168:241a-7: stobs bcu ldan pa'i gdung bcas gzhan gang yin pa de la'ang spyis phyag 'tshal //
T01D1168:241a-8: ti se gangs ri gangs can la gnas mand'a ra dang ri rab rtse //
T01D1168:241a-9: klu gnas rnam rgyal nod sbyin gnas dang rig 'dzin grub pa'i gnas //
T01D1168:241a-10: tshangs dang khyab 'jug gnas dang phyugs bdag nyi ma zla ba'i gnas //
T01D1168:241a-11: stobs bcu ldan pa'i mchod rten gzhan gang yin pa de la'ang spyis phyag 'tshal //
T01D1168:241a-12: stobs bcu las byung rin chen snying can mchod rten brgyad po gdung bcas bum las gru ba //
T01D1168:241a-13: sol ba de bzhin rin chen mchod rten gangs dang dngul 'dra rab mdzes pa //
T01D1168:241a-14: sa 'og sa stengs lha yul rtser bzhugs mchod rten ji snyed ma lus dang //
T01D1168:241a-15: sangs rgyas sku gzugs gang bzhugs de la nyin re bzhin du spyi bos phyag bya'o //
T01D1168:241a-16: gnas chen po brgyad kyi mchod rten la phyag 'tshal
T01D1168:241a-17: ba'i bstod pa kha che'i rgyal po shr'i ha ri
T01D1168:241a-18: sha de bas yum gyi ched du mdzad pa rdzogs
T01D1168:241a-20: / rgya gar gyi mkhan po r'a dza shr'i dzny'a na mi tra dang /
